main event: Civilians observed two unidentified flying objects over St Paul, Minnesota on July 16, 1966.
interesting points: The sightings involved a green light in front and a reddish light behind,The object was described as traveling at tremendous speed and then slowing down on the second night,The lights disappeared suddenly as if turned off,The event was witnessed by multiple neighbors,The sightings occurred over a two-night span with consistent observations.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects with green and reddish lights
witness description: Civilians and neighbors observing from their backyard
